abstract: Prosecutors in Lancaster County, Neb, say evidence does not support bringing charges against Nebraska quarterback Tommy Armstrong and receiver Jordan Westerkamp after rape accusations.
lead_paragraph: Prosecutors announced that they had decided not to bring charges after an accusation that a rape had occurred this month at the home of Nebraska quarterback Tommy Armstrong and receiver Jordan Westerkamp.
